  <name>MetaImGUI</name>
  <summary>ImGui Application Template</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      MetaImGUI is a professional template for creating ImGui-based desktop applications.
      It provides a complete infrastructure including cross-platform build system,
      CI/CD automation, testing framework, and professional packaging.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Modern C++20 codebase</li>
      <li>Cross-platform support (Linux, Windows, macOS)</li>
      <li>ImGui v1.92.4 integration</li>
      <li>Automated CI/CD with GitHub Actions</li>
      <li>Built-in update checking</li>
      <li>Configuration management</li>
      <li>Logging system</li>
      <li>Testing framework with Catch2</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

